{"tid":144892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港高鐵站將建支方戰術支援組辦公室及羈留設施","createTime":"2017-03-05T19:58:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-07T01:17:31.000Z","uid":22054,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7936545051bd36ded84ea5b1f9cac5a0e9d3ac60","tid":144892,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T19:58:01.000Z","msg":"明報獲得兩份高鐵西九龍總站詳細設計文件修訂版本，文件分別在2015年尾及2016年初提交予政府部門。<br />\n<br />\n文件內的圖則顯示，早在2015年11月，港鐵已於西九龍總站B2及B3兩層，詳細規劃一地兩檢設施，包括MCIQ Office（Mainland Customs, Immigration and Quarantine Office），即內地清關、出入境及檢疫設施辦公室，當中包括羈留設施、可容納121至200人的職員休息室、監察及戰術支援組辦公室等，兩層辦公室的面積合共約9.2萬平方呎。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170305/s00001/1488724509981\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170305%2Fs00001%2F1488724509981&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvNr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=34d34051\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170305%2Fs00001%2F1488724509981&h=da3de47f\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170305/s00001/1488724509981</a>"},{"pid":"d83f4652124fdcf956e2c784db75555be45b261b","tid":144892,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T20:45:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b87d655fabe3619355765a0a547f3b3a0dbb9c6","tid":144892,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T21:15:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d025ef8245c680f61a3a4b01b3cb0600cd80f08c","tid":144892,"uid":49955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-05T21:23:59.000Z","msg":"冇人理架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"273a0354b4ed768e1a09e8bafc498c779939cae2","tid":144892,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"